    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>「我是清纯的幽灵，奈特魅芽唷～！」</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VTuber「<strong>なぃとめあ</strong>」本人主演！融合<strong>ASMR</strong>的视觉小说游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和幽灵「魅芽」来一场充满魅力的约会吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部分台词以ASMR录製，享受与魅芽的亲密又甜蜜的互动吧🤍</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326910/extras/c3ceafb3ccf2e2424fef94e0a5ea8009.avif?t=1733929239\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326910/extras_big/c3ceafb3ccf2e2424fef94e0a5ea8009.avif?t=1733929239 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>🤍剧情简介🤍</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >清纯的幽灵少女带来的奇妙日常——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >疲于工作的主角面前，突然出现了非常清纯的幽灵女孩「魅芽」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >儘管是幽灵，她却尽全力想安慰主人公，为了让主人公安眠，但……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次都让我感到心跳加速。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从公园到拉麵店，接着是试胆挑战、旅馆，两人一起度过了约会的每一天。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >脑海里总有些记忆无法回想起来，或许正是某些原因让「魅芽」无法成佛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两人之间究竟有着怎样的过去——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是不是也想体验，和「魅芽」共同度过那段神秘且充满甜蜜的时光呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>🤍角色🤍</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326910/extras/22840bce75ed84298f6ca1bd8b187046.avif?t=1733929239\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奈特魅芽（CV:なぃとめあ）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了给工作疲惫的主角能安稳入睡而出现，一个非常清纯的耳朵舔舔幽灵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于生前记忆很模糊的关係，导致她无法成佛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>🤍 SPECIAL THANKS 🤍</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主演・主角：奈特魅芽</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >绘师：ひさぎ</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >编剧：みるくやしき</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👻👻👻<strong>亲爱的ちゅなぃと各位！！</strong>👻👻👻</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>🤍推荐给这样的人🤍</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅喜欢VTuber和ASMR的人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅想被可爱女孩宠爱的人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅希望与女生一起体验心跳加速感觉的人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>🐇 小说游戏品牌「Rabbitfoot」 🐇</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326910/extras/625dee9b413a2b91ca25292e181ec90a.avif?t=1733929239\" width=616 height=163 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是专门以活动中的YouTube或VTuber以游戏内角色身份，于视觉小说游戏中登场的品牌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了会以本人的名称或暱称登场之外、还能享受到与实况或影片分享时不同的一面、最大的魅力就是让玩家更能感受到“本命推”更加接近自己的游戏性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>🤍官方网站🤍</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>⚠️关于实况直播与影片上传的规则⚠️</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
